fields.name: Bulbasaur
fields.bio: Bulbasaur (Japanese: フシギダネ Fushigidane) is a dual-type Grass/Poison Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves into Ivysaur starting at level 16, which evolves into Venusaur starting at level 32.

fields.name: Ivysaur
fields.bio: Ivysaur (Japanese: フシギソウ Fushigisou) is a dual-type Grass/Poison Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Bulbasaur starting at level 16 and evolves into Venusaur.

fields.name: Venusaur
fields.bio: Venusaur (Japanese: フシギバナ Fushigibana) is a dual-type Grass/Poison Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Ivysaur starting at level 32. It is the final form of Bulbasaur. It can Mega Evolve into Mega Venusaur using the Venusaurite.

fields.name: Charmander
fields.bio: Charmander (Japanese: ヒトカゲ Hitokage) is a Fire-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves into Charmeleon starting at level 16, which evolves into Charizard starting at level 36.

fields.name: Charmeleon
fields.bio: Charmeleon (Japanese: リザード Lizardo) is a Fire-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Charmander starting at level 16 and evolves into Charizard starting at level 36.

fields.name: Charizard
fields.bio: Charizard (Japanese: リザードン Lizardon) is a dual-type Fire/Flying Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Charmeleon starting at level 36. It is the final form of Charmander.

fields.name: Charizard
fields.bio: Charizard (Japanese: リザードン Lizardon) is a dual-type Fire/Flying Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Charmeleon starting at level 36. It is the final form of Charmander.

fields.name: Squirtle
fields.bio: Squirtle (Japanese: ゼニガメ Zenigame) is a Water-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves into Wartortle starting at level 16, which evolves into Blastoise starting at level 36.

fields.name: Wartortle
fields.bio: Wartortle (Japanese: カメール Kameil) is a Water-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Squirtle starting at level 16 and evolves into Blastoise starting at level 36.

fields.name: Blastoise
fields.bio: Blastoise (Japanese: カメックス Kamex) is a Water-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Wartortle starting at level 36. It is the final form of Squirtle.

fields.name: Pikachu
fields.bio: Pikachu (Japanese: ピカチュウ Pikachu) is an Electric-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I. It evolves from Pichu when leveled up with high friendship and evolves into Raichu when exposed to a Thunder Stone.
